## DESCRIPTION
## Simple spring, damper, and load system. What damping constant will make the system critically damped?
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('Critically damped', 'Free damped Vibration','')
## DBsubject(Dynamics)
## DBchapter(Vibration)
## DBsection()
## Date(2020-6-30)
## Author(Daniel Youm)
## Institution(University of British Columbia)
## Level(Beginner)
